\begin_layout Section*
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Multi-criteria Decision Analysis (MCDA) which also can be call as "Multiple
 Criteria Decision-Making" or "Multi-criteria Decision Aiding'' in English
 or "Analyse Multicritère" in French is an exciting field which has seen
 many achievements including increasing number of research papers, books,
 and theories over the years since the 70s 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "pugnaire1992multicriteria,roy2005paradigms"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For many decision makers, MCDA is an excellent tool in getting comprehensive
 insight information when solving a decision problem especially when there
 are many different factors which are taken into account 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "pugnaire1992multicriteria,roy2005paradigms"

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this thesis, we will show to the readers how to incorporate Artificial
 Neural Network (ANN) in MCDA 
